<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Dietrich von Egloffstein</head><p>Der Rat bittet für Konrad und Alheid Eschenloher, Bürger zu Nürnberg, wegen Mähens ihrer Wiese zu Pretzfeld und Erntens ihrer Äcker durch den Adressaten um Herausgabe der Früchte.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_91" id="44r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_91_r2l2"><expan>Dyetrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Eglofſtein cʒum Eglofſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r2l3">geſeſʒen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_91_r2l4">Lıeber Dyetrich vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Conrad Eſſchenloer / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r2l5">vvie daʒ Jr Jm vnd <expan>Alheid<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeiner <expan>elich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wirtin 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu vvie daʒ Jr Jn </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r2l6">ir wıſen cʒu Pretfeldt abgemeͣet / vnd Jn ir ecker 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu </del> doſelbſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r2l7">abgeſnẏten habt / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> dem </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_91_line_1574669778350_422">den </ab></add> <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r2l9">vnd ſein wirtin an <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſeınen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_91_line_1574669786813_431">Jren </ab></add> wiſen vnd eckern mit <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>cʒugehor<ex>ung</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r2l10">
<del rend="strikethrough">vngeheh </del> vngehindert / vnd Jn das ir das darauff gevvachſen iſt <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r2l11">laſſen wöllet / durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / ewr <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r2l12"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒuvviſſen <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_91" id="44r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Dyetrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Eglofstein, czum Eglofstein
                        geseszen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Dyetrich, uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Conrad
                        Esschenloer, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, wie daz ir im und
                                <expan>Alheid<ex>en</ex></expan>, seiner
                            <expan>elich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wirtin, ir wisen czu Pretfeldt abgemeͣet
                        und in ir ecker doselbst abgesnyten habt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir <add>den</add>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, und sein wirtin an
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>iren</add> wisen und eckern mit <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>czugehor<ex>ung</ex></expan> ungehindert und in das ir, das darauff
                        gewachsen ist, <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen wöllet durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. Ewr <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> czuwissen.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
